name: 4REALZA COIN
description: 4realza's main utility is its support of newly launch crypto projects. why you ask? Fact is, 90% of cryptocurrencies will not survive a market crash. A good portion of new crypto projects lack any real utility or contribution and will more than likely fail leaving its investors down & out. Good news is there are some new projects with good intentions & want to contribute. But lack the backing and support needed to grow and flourish. 4REALZA aims to curve this
